name: Inktober
description: At 64 beautifully printed black and white pages, this book collects the thirty-one drawings I did for Inktober and brings together several other drawings from my projects and sketchbooks. Everything from dinosaurs and robots, to salty old sailors and mad scientists find a home in this book. AND if you want to find out what ever happened to RoyalBot EP-43 and the Queen's blowfish, the exciting conclusion is immortalized within these inky pages. You can see all the art from Inktober plus more in my Instagram feed HERE. 9.75 x 7.5 in 64 Pages Black and White SHIPPING Domestic Shipping: 6.00 USD Canada: 15.00 USD International Shipping (excluding Canada): 25.00 USD Books are packed in a bubble wrap sleeve and then securely fitted into a cardboard mailing box.
